  by Tech Worker’s Coalition Canada
  (https://techworkerscoalition.org/canada/)\n\nDrop by for a virtual
  coffee hour on Sunday mornings to chat with fellow tech workers about
  what’s on your mind and to learn more about the Tech Worker’s
  Coalition. TWC considers anyone who is involved in the production and
  maintenance of digital technology to be a tech worker\, whether you are a
  bike courier working at a food delivery app service\, a designer\, a
  software engineer\, a product owner\, a data labeller or a content
  moderator. Hope to see you there!
END:VEVENT
